# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# BUILD CONFIGURATION
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# No environment variables are currently required for the design system package.
#
# This is a design system package that provides:
#   - Tailwind CSS configuration and presets
#   - Shared theme variables (dark brown/black with metallic gold accents)
#   - Reusable UI component styles
#   - Typography settings
#
# When consuming this package in other projects, those projects may have their
# own environment variable requirements.
#
# ==============================================================================

# ==============================================================================
# USAGE NOTES
# ==============================================================================
#
# This design system package is used as a dependency in other SmartFlow Systems
# projects. It does not require any environment variables to function.
#
# To use in your project:
#   1. Install the package: npm install @smartflow/design-system
#   2. Import the Tailwind preset in your tailwind.config.js
#   3. Import theme CSS variables in your global styles
#
# See README.md for detailed integration instructions.
#
# ==============================================================================
